## High priority:

As a user I want to be able to add a vink to the app so I can find it easily later.
As a user I want to be able to browse my vinks to find things to read.


## Medium priority:

As a user I want to be able to delete the vinks if I decide not to read them.
As a user I want to be able to modify the vinks.
As a user I want to be able differentiate between different types of vinks to find them easily.
As a user I want to be able to sort the vinks according to different categories.
As a user I want to be able to filter my vinks according to their tags and other variables.

## Low priority:

As a user I want to be able to browse my vinks through a browser to access them easily.
As a user I want to add vinks using only a youtube url.
As a user I want to be able to classify my vinks to read and unread vinks (low prio)









